Brought to you by: Happy Croissant Scans!

『Sometimes, your future gets decided by just one moment.』

The whole kingdom of Jes&uacute;s fell into a state of shock after hearing the news of Queen Mary Trizia&rsquo;s Suicide.

While everyone praised Mary Trizia for being an excellent queen, whilst her older twin brother, Rafael Evans, was most suspicious of her death.

&lsquo;It can only be you. No one else can save me other than you.&rsquo; 

These words and the image of his sister screaming those words while approaching him bare-footed remained in his head. Rafael ventures out in search after his relatives for the first time in his life, to attend Mary&rsquo;s funeral.

But in the place where they found Mary&rsquo;s body, Rafael finds a note&hellip;

&ldquo;Lift up your face.&rdquo;
Wanting to find the killer of Mary, Rafael disguises himself as the new queen consort, Anne-Mary La Shore and meets the king &lsquo;Ivry.&rsquo;

That moment marked the start of an unprecedented fate.
The unexpected end of his sister who wasn&rsquo;t like her younger self, and who he believed would find happiness&hellip;

What was the &lsquo;hell&rsquo; that his sister dropped into?
And what will change after Rafael and Ivry meet?
